data.description: : 3 bedroom 1 bath rancher. Full walkout basement. Two car attached carport. Deck, front porch. Low maintenance brick veneer exterior. Property is owned by the US Dept. of HUD. HUD Case # 481-348125. FHA financing IE (Insured Escrow). 203 K Eligible (YES). Subject to an FHA appraisal. Buyer selects closing agent/firm. Seller makes no representations or warranties as to property condition. HUD homes are sold as -is Equal Housing Opportunity. Seller may contribute up to 3% for buyer's closing costs, upon buyer request. Housing type, age, square footage, lot size, total rooms, bedroom and bath counts per HUD appraisal. Taxes, septic  per Monroe County. Water source per City of Tellico Plains Water Dept. Buyer(s) to verify all information.
